trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity" /> class encapsulates the transport security settings for the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity" /> 클래스는 MSMQ(메시지 큐) 통합 채널용 전송 보안 설정을 캡슐화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The Message Queuing integration channel enables [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] applications to communicate with existing Message Queuing applications.
trans-unit.target: 메시지 큐 통합 채널을 사용하면 [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] 응용 프로그램을 기존 메시지 큐 응용 프로그램과 통신하도록 할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode" /> that is associated with the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel.
trans-unit.target: 메시지 큐 통합 채널과 연결된 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode" />를 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode" /> that is associated with the Message Queuing integration channel.

<xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode> is an enumeration that contains the following values: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode.None> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode.Transport>.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> that is associated with the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel.
trans-unit.target: 메시지 큐 통합 채널과 연결된 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> that is associated with the Message Queuing integration channel.
<xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity> encapsulates the security settings for the Message Queuing integration transport.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity>는 메시지 큐 통합 전송을 위한 보안 설정을 캡슐화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The settings are the same for both the Message Queuing integration and queued transports.
trans-unit.target: 설정은 메시지 큐 통합 및 대기 중인 전송에서 모두 동일합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity> enables you to set the Authentication Mode, Encryption Algorithm, Secure Hash Algorithm, and Protection Level.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity>를 사용하여 인증 모드, 암호화 알고리즘, 보안 해시 알고리즘 및 보호 수준을 설정할 수 있습니다.
